Example of compound filter:

{code}
......
"accounting-groups":{
"base-dn":"OU=Money Office,OU=Users,DC=wu-tang,DC=com",
"id-attribute":"cn",
"member-attribute":"member",
"selection":{
"filter":"(&(objectClass=top)(objectClass=group)(memberOf=*))",
},
"groups":{
"base-dn":"OU=Money Office,OU=Users,DC=wu-tang,DC=com",
"id-attribute":"cn",
"member-attribute":"member",
"selection":{
"filter":"(&(objectClass=group)(objectClass=top)(!memberOf=*))" 
}
},
.....
{code}

Hey [~sjones] and [~tjcramer],

