Syncing of account, groups and users were done correctly.  After testing this, I am confident this is a LIC file format issue. I will convert this to a feature request for a tool to confirm the proper format of the LIC file.  Please let me know if there are any questions.

Additional thought on this - maybe the check could be done as part of the euca-modify-property command when you are uploading the LIC file.

{code}
/usr/sbin/euca-modify-property -f authentication.ldap_integration_configuration=<lic_filename.lic>
{code}

Instead of returning the full LIC file and what the sync was set to before, maybe change it to displaying that the file is in the correct format, then the previous state of the sync.  Thoughts?
